    <h3>Tag</h3>
    <p1> Tag is a game which is easy to play, many people love it and play it every day you only need people for this game.
    </p1><br>
    <h3>How many people you need to play.</h3>
    <p1> You need at least two people including you to play this game but you can have as many people as you want.</p1>
    <h3>How you play the game.</h3>
    <p1> You have one tagger 
         everyone else is running away from the tagger. The taggers job is to tag other people by taping them.
        Only the tagger can tag people. If you tag someone your not the tagger anymore and the person you tagged is now the tagger and everyone has to run away from the new tagger.</p1><br>
